d States was greatly enhanced by the fame of  President Abraham Lincoln  (  1809–65 )."],"variants":[{"name":"Avrom","meanings":["Yiddish form of   Abraham ."]},{"name":"Avraham","meanings":["modern Hebrew form of   Abraham ."]}]}],"historicEvents":[{"id":1356698,"age":40,"year":"1572","julianDay":2295221,"description":"William of Orange was recognized as viceroy of Holland, Friesland and Utrecht.","jurisdictionLevel":1},{"id":1356699,"age":41,"year":"1573","julianDay":2295587,"description":"The siege of Leiden between the rebels and the Spanish. 1574 The dikes were opened allowing a Dutch fleet to sail over the flood waters and rescue Leiden.","jurisdictionLevel":1}],"lifeSummary":"When Jacobus Abraham Loosje was born in 1532, in Zeeland, Netherlands, his father, Cornelius Marcus Loosje, was 32 and his mother, Antejlt Vertman, was 21. He married Maretje Janszen in 1557, in Zeeland, Netherlands. They were the parents of at least 2 sons and 2 daughters. He died in 1579, in his hometown, at the age of 47."},"et":{"1532–1579":"1532–1579","1537–1562":"1537–1562","1540–1549":"1540–1549","1544–1603":"1544–1603","1548–1625":"1548–1625","1530–1582":"1530–1582","1563–1609":"1563–1609","1567–1618":"1567–1618","1569–1618":"1569–1618","1557–Female":"1557–Surnud","1500–1572":"1500–1572","1511–1568":"1511–1568","1582":"1582","1579":"1579","1557":"1557","       1557":"1557","1511":"1511","1532":"1532","1530":"1530","1573":"1573","1618":"1618","1537":"1537","1572":"1572","       1572":"1572","1569":"1569","       1567":"1567","1568":"1568","1567":"1567","August 1563":"august 1563","1500":"1500","1544":"1544","1563":"1563","1540":"1540","1562":"1562","1609":"1609","1549":"1549","1625":"1625","1548":"1548","1603":"1603",",, Zeeland, Netherlands":"Zeeland, Madalmaad","Zeeland, Netherlands":"Zeeland, Madalmaad"},"fi":{"1532–1579":"1532–1579","1537–1562":"1537–1562","1540–1549":"1540–1549","1544–1603":"1544–1603","1548–1625":"1548–1625","1530–1582":"1530–1582","1563–1609":"1563–1609","1